<style>
  .gp {
  background-position: right bottom;
  background-repeat: no-repeat;
  display: block;
  font-size: 15px;
  font-weight: bold;
  color: #fff;
  padding: 9px 20px;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
  border-radius: 2px;
  box-shadow: none;
background-color: #eb5e4c;
background-image: url(/assets/img/icons/login-google-icon.png);
  
  }
</style>
<div class="inner-head" style="background-image:url('/assets/img/calendar.png');padding-bottom: 27px;">
                <div class="container">
                  <h1 class="entry-title">회원정보를 입력해주세요.</h1>
                    <p class="description" style="color:#fff;">
                      수업 시간표 설정을 하기 전에 성함과 이메일 주소를 입력해주세요. 구글 계정이 있으신 분은 구글 계정으로 간단히 로그인이 가능합니다.

                    </p>
                    <br>
                    <div class="breadcrumb">
                      <div class="col-md-12 col-sm-12 ">
                        <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-6 col-md-offset-3 col-sm-offset-3">
                          <a href="<%=user_omniauth_authorize_path(:google_oauth2) %>" class="login-op-btn grad-btn ln-tr gp">Login with Google Account</a>
                        </div>
                      </div><!-- end GP login -->
                    </div>
                </div><!-- End container -->
            </div><!-- End Inner Page Head -->

            <div class="clearfix"></div>

            <section class="login-page fadeInDown-animation" style="padding-top:25px; padding-bottom:20px;">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2">
                            <div class="login-form register">
                                <div class="login-title">
                                    <span class="icon"><i class="fa fa-group"></i></span>
                                    <span class="text">성함과 이메일로 등록</span>
                                </div><!-- End Title -->
                                <form method="post" action="/" id="register-form">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-6">
                                            <div class="input">
                                                <input type="text" id="reg_username" class="username-input" placeholder="Name">
                                            </div>
                                        </div><!-- end username -->
                                        <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-6">
                                            <div class="input">
                                                <input type="email" id="reg_email" class="email-input" placeholder="Email">
                                            </div>
                                        </div><!-- end email -->
                                        <div class="col-md-12">
                                            <div class="input clearfix">
                                                <input type="submit" id="reg_submit" class="submit-input grad-btn ln-tr" value="Register">
                                            </div>
                                        </div><!-- end submit -->
                                    </div><!-- end row -->
                                </form><!-- End form -->
                            </div><!-- end login form -->
                        </div><!-- end col-md-8/offset -->
                    </div><!-- end row -->
                  </div><!-- end container -->
            </section><!-- End Register Page -->

            <div class="clearfix"></div>
